name: cyhorinX.1
description:
Cyhorin is a Hak living in the state of Nervos on the planet Porton in the binary solar system. He protects the Krotep stone given to his people. He made himself an armor of Boristar steel. There is no weapon that can pierce that armor yet. That's why he is called immortal.
Name : Cyhorin
Tribe : Hakir 
Planet : Porton
Weapon of Choice: Ax
